assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Renaissance United Limited, an investment holding company, engages in various business activities in Singapore, China, the United States of America, Taiwan, Europe, and internationally. develops, turnkey contracts, and invests in oil and gas, and environment, and industrial infrastructure projects worldwide. The company operates through five segments: Infrastructure Development and Turnkey Construction; Property Development; Gas Distribution; Electronics and Trading; and Investment Securities Trading. It engages in infrastructure and residential estate development, engineering, construction, and warehousing services; assembling and trading of semiconductor products; and providing consultancy services in semi-conductor industry. The company also manufactures, assembles, installs, maintains, repairs, and deals in electronic components; trades in investment securities; and distributes and transports natural gas. In addition, it is involved in agency and distribution of semi-conductor back-end equipment, such as vision inspection systems and test systems; and provision of interest-free loans. The company was formerly known as Ipco International Limited and changed its name to Renaissance United Limited in December 2018. Renaissance United Limited was incorporated in 1992 and is based in Singapore.
